item.content:encoded:
Hi Friends! Welcome to my new portfolio site for my work. I’m happy to be on fancy WordPress, but I’ve also lost all my link juice from the previous iteration of my website oops.

But it would be super appreciated if you linked to this site so I can get some link juice back! Let me know what you think of the new presentation.

Happy 2013
Cheers
Steven
